reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 31, 2024
reviews.reviewText: It is perfect for my guest room/office. Wouldn’t recommend as a full dresser though as the drawers are a bit small. But for me it’s perfect

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 10, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Super cute dresser, directions aren’t that clear in the beginning. needs to come with another tool. Took way longer that expected to put together.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 5, 2024
reviews.reviewText: My hubby said it was good quality & easy to put together but…the smell has never gone away. It’s unpleasant & strong. Also, it’s a much darker pink than pictured. A wee bit gawdy. Would not recommend purchasing. We bought another from a different company except it’s gray. Does not smell at all.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 8, 2024
reviews.reviewText: I ordered 4 of these cabinets and all of them came in one piece, even though a couple of the boxes had holes. My husband was also able to put them together quite easily. I wish the drawers were a little deeper, but you get what you pay for and for the price, I absolutely love them! It almost appears as if it's one large dresser. With that being said, I couldn't be happier with way they look.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 21, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 1.0 out of 5 stars CUTE but NOT worth it
reviews.reviewText: This dresser looks SO cute online and once built. HOWVERRRR, this dresser took a FULL day to build due to broken pieces. The main center rod was missing the second whole which would have made the dresser more sturdy. The circle nail holders are so loose they kept and keep popping out when I move the dresser. There are multiple scratches and stains as well. I tried to contact the company because I wanted at least a partial of credit due to the broken and missing pieces, however, the only options they provided were a replacement or a return. Both require me to break it down to send it back. I don't really post reviews but thought I should warn people that if you want something will last and be worth the money do NOT buy this product.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 22, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 2.0 out of 5 stars 2*as they are pretty & will work for my purposes, missing 3* due to errors with directions& product
reviews.reviewText: The media could not be loaded. Holy cow, the directions are awful. There are errors and zero written directions or notes. Step 1 if you don't see the lever give it a bit of a tug. Step 2 there is a mess up you will need A and C to attach the support bars, parts and holes match A and C, direction show A and A. Not all part were labeled for the drawer sides match the lines and big holes. Have photos of the A and C spot. About half of the B part holes are slightly too big so they will wiggle loose and unscrew them self, video shows the looseness I am gluing them in place. This piece will work for light use needs but not advised for daily use things like clothing. All 3 of mine had the same issues thru our. Took so long out together. They are pretty and I am storing craft supplies in them but be advised they will be a head ache to put together and keep together.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 28, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Good dresser for the price
reviews.reviewText: I really loved the look of this dresser online, so I bought two! I was nervous since there weren’t any reviews for the 6 drawer one, so I was really crossing my fingers that it’d be good. I got them delivered, and assembled the first one within 2.5 hrs by myself and the second one took me 2 hrs. I don’t have experience building furniture at all, but the instructions were clear enough. I built both of them without any issues! Just time consuming, but what do you expect for this price? To my surprise, all the drawers were lined up, nothing was dinged, and it works as intended! Also have to note that I’m always weary about buying furniture online, because shipping causes damage. NOTHING was even slightly damaged or dinged, so I really applaud the packaging. I will say it’s on the smaller side compared to standard dressers — the drawers are on the shallow side. It fit my needs though, so that’s fine for me! Overall, I’m satisfied with the product. It met my expectations, and it provides the storage I need.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 11, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Worth the current price!
reviews.reviewText: It was not hard to put together. The drawers glide so nicely! There’s not a lot of room in the drawers, the dresser is somewhat small, but it gets the job done in a toddlers room! Overall I love this dresser!
